{
  "stem": "5375.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we started moving, and then we went all night long.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How long did it take to get to the Ukraine?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we stopped a few places before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We arrived there about-- we arrived in Briansk, Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There, a lot of, especially [INAUDIBLE] Hungarian people know about it, but this was the biggest punishment what they could give the Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were dying like flies there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Dysentery, ?] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all kinds of-- After being there, we arrived there, they put us to pick up landmines what the Russians left over.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1943.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was already in the fall of 1943.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We picked up landmines.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had dogs what they smelled out the mine, where it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then we had to go-- they told us what to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to go to unscrew to take away the-- the earth from around it, and to unscrew the two screws where they really detonated the mine.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where that-- that was the wire what really start it up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we throw away the fuses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once a week, Sunday, we exploded them, the land mines.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything was going all right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How many people did you work with?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How many people were in your group?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With ?] 224 people, that was the-- when we arrived there, we were 224 people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But one night, the partisans, the Russian partisans came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they made a raid over the place in the woods there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They surrounded the whole area, and they started shooting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were-- we had a captain, a Hungarian captain.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had about 10 soldiers-- sergeants, and so on, and so on, corporals.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] they were taking care of us, like I told you.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
